{"tid":1868224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個罷工醫護嘅心聲","createTime":"2020-02-07T12:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T12:57:43.000Z","uid":338092,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d43d475475aa4eeb5f5a2d675972ddef043f79b","tid":1868224,"uid":338092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"第一次出post<br />\nSorry 1999<br />\n<br />\n我係一名醫護<br />\n參與左一連五日罷工<br />\n亦都諗左好耐投左中止罷工<br />\n<br />\n好多人笑9我地揸住HA春袋都縮<br />\n其實我就係覺得HA高層係太監根本冇春袋<br />\n預約手術做唔到門診睇唔到對佢地黎講有咩所謂<br />\n全醫院啲人死哂佢地都會照出糧<br />\n<br />\n香港人嘅春袋，只有錢<br />\n你罷工令佢蝕錢，就會有成績<br />\n用人命做賭注我地一定輸俾佢<br />\nThey don't give a shxt<br />\n<br />\n我地罷工嘅心理壓力真係好大<br />\n唔係驚佢秋後<br />\n係真係驚影響到病人<br />\n<br />\n我以為我地開始罷工係一場接力賽<br />\n點知冇人肯接棒<br />\n逼我地跑馬拉松<br />\n我地唔識跑<br />\n成日叫人唔好道德綁架我地<br />\n只係叫我地繼續又唔幫手何嘗唔係<br />\n<br />\n最後無論我地有冇罷工，我地都係同一個信念<br />\n希望呢場疫情死傷可以減到最低<br />\n但似乎都冇咩可能<br />\n<br />\n香港人，自求多福"},{"pid":"58e9de666ec86eff453726d09c7113e53c91b803","tid":1868224,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n話驚秋後算賬好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到變左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7b9348d95acf7d7d09cfe7e47cb6bf41820be18c","tid":1868224,"uid":197314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80078a71b0657b2fa7f9fba4f639e0d7d9562254","tid":1868224,"uid":335694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fe63eda0f373642047b0e3cb6a8bb8f2fa671f","tid":1868224,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"支持醫護任何決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=